delta d = d_Dp - u_Dn = epsilon(x) * d_p - epsilon(x) *u_n
        = epsilon(x) * [d_p - u_n]

delta u = epsilon(x) *[u_p - d_n]


delta d - delta u = epsilon(x)[ d_p - u_n - u_p + d_n]  ---1

u_vDp = epsilon(x) * u_vp
d_vDp = epsilon(x) * d_vp

u_vDp + d_vDp = epsilon(x} *[u_vp + d_vp]---2

1 divide 2 will cancel epsilon

